{
  "stem": "2713.2",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And not only did he send the medicine, he sent a loaf of bread with it as well.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I just couldn't believe it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I just couldn't believe it because I-- I was with him for quite a while, and I knew the things that he was doing.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- I-- I just don't understand why.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I can't understand.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this is what he did.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So it took another few days or so, and I tried to get-- I felt a bit better, and I could see already.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I used to take this medicine.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't know what it was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They used to give me this medicine, and I felt better.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But mainly, it was amazing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Used to-- when people got sick on typhus, when healthy boys went in, they came out.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Then it was a time when you were a bit skinnier.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You just had no chance of surviving.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And there were different times.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Unfortunately, my brother got sick after me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When he got sick, I said to him, look, try to get out from the hospital as soon as possible because there you can't survive.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "With those bugs and things, it's impossible to survive.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was going to see him every day in the hospital, when I-- from work in the morning and then at night.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And everything was all right.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[SOBBING] One morning I went in, and I could see he's feeling every day a bit better.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was quite happy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then when I came back at night from the camp, from the-- from work, he was dead.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And what I found out afterwards that they injected all the people that they were in the hospital with methylated spirit.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the doctor's name was Cohen, a Jewish doctor.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
